metadata.name: Free Fallin'
metadata.description:
Free Fallinâ€™ is a bright and bold oil pastel drawing that evokes feelings of joy and bliss. The composition is inspired by the bold and expressive styles of 90s art, with an emphasis on vibrant colors and playful forms.

The overall effect is one of euphoria and excitement for the future, with a sense of energy and positivity that is impossible to ignore. The use of collage elements adds an extra layer of texture and interest, creating a dynamic and engaging visual experience. 

Overall this piece is a celebration of the joy and beauty of life, and a reminder to embrace the possibilities of the future with open arms.
